<p>Pipe functions transform values using the <code>|</code> operator. Functions can be chained for complex transformations.</p>

<h2>Basic Syntax</h2>
<pre>{open}$variable | functionName{close}
{open}$variable | functionName('parameter'){close}
{open}$variable | func1 | func2 | func3{close}</pre>

